name: DiabetesMellitusDisorder
title: Diabetes Mellitus Disorder
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Diabetes mellitus),(Data Element Scope: Diabetes which may require home glucose monitoring medical equipment, as defined by U.S. Centers for Medicare and Medicaid.),(Inclusion Criteria: Type 1, Type 2, gestational, 
drug or chemical induced diabetes 
mellitus),(Exclusion Criteria: Diabetes insipidus)
